OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAnother very warm day on
OL,6,FTuesday, although sunshine likely to
OL,7,Fbe more hazy than of late. A very
OL,8,Fsmall chance of the odd shower
OL,9,Fdeveloping later but most staying dry.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FRemaining very warm with plenty more
OL,13,Fsunshine, although an increasing risk
OL,14,Fof some showers and thunderstorms at
OL,15,Ftimes. Lighter winds than Monday and
OL,16,FTuesday adding to the warm feel.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
